{"tid":2182182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"光榮冰室賣《蘋果》 市民撐場  「不想敢作敢為報章受打壓」","createTime":"2020-08-31T06:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T06:59:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10875c2af94272f46d92dbf3a88529383e9931ac","tid":2182182,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/SJNOSNS6TZBJZH5EZNPFZFG2MY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FSJNOSNS6TZBJZH5EZNPFZFG2MY%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=19ef2313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FSJNOSNS6TZBJZH5EZNPFZFG2MY%2F&h=2cf68282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/SJNOSNS6TZBJZH5EZNPFZFG2MY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n光榮冰室賣《蘋果》 市民撐場 <br />\n「不想敢作敢為報章受打壓」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】繼阿布泰國生活百貨旗下11間分店前日起售賣《蘋果日報》，抵銷國企華潤萬家旗下VanGO便利店突然停售約千份《蘋果》的數量後，光榮冰室六間分店今起亦出售《蘋果》，預計每間分店賣30至50份；其中深井店昨率先有售，不少熱心市民專程到冰室只為買《蘋果》，亦有街坊買早餐兼買《蘋果》，直言：「特登嚟支持！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NuzH2UITQHcq7le1Sl1_F6DA1mE=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/25SHCBEEKZEM3KA23YTGCSFCQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNuzH2UITQHcq7le1Sl1_F6DA1mE%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F25SHCBEEKZEM3KA23YTGCSFCQQ.jpg&h=f488fbaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■光榮冰室昨在深井店率先售賣《蘋果日報》，吸引多人購買。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n街坊不滿VanGO停售<br />\n<br />\n光榮冰室深井店昨率先有售100份《蘋果》，並以購入價8元發售，前來購買的市民絡繹不絕。光榮冰室表示，不希望香港一份敢作敢為的報章在港受到打壓，所以選擇成為《蘋果》的銷售點，由今日起六間分店將售賣《蘋果》，預計每間分店出售30至50份；若反應熱烈，將會擴展至全部分店。<br />\n<br />\n不少市民昨早到光榮冰室深井店買《蘋果》，部份人邊堂食早餐邊讀報，亦有市民買外賣兼買一份，甚至有街坊專程只買一份，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n梁先生抱着愛犬到光榮買外賣，「知道有《蘋果》就一齊買埋」，又指「《蘋果》喺好多地方都俾人打壓，呢度（冰室）有得賣更加方便大家。」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ji7Jhxxyjj_-oafIBono21RU410=/1820x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N6IEQDVRXJG6ZGGETCFHDNICII.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJi7Jhxxyjj_-oafIBono21RU410%3D%2F1820x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN6IEQDVRXJG6ZGGETCFHDNICII.jpg&h=6846f913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梁先生手抱愛犬，到光榮冰室買外賣兼買《蘋果》。"}]}